dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Mount Boardman quadrangle, Santa Clara, Alameda, San Joaquin & Stanislaus counties, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Mount Boardman CA 1996. NIMA 1758 IV NW, series V895." "First printing, July 2006." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references", most recent published in 1996.
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
